    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head rend="align(center)">Richard Jones Will.</head>
                <p>In the Name of God Amen. I <persName type="author">Richard <surname>Jones</surname></persName> of <placeName>Charles County
                <lb/>in the province of Maryland</placeName> lying very sick and weake but of perfect
                    <lb/>minde &amp; memory blessed be to God for I doe hereby make this my last
                    <lb/>will and testament in manner &amp; form followeth.
                </p>
                <p><unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> I commit my soule to God the father of our Lord Jesus Christ by whome
                    <lb/><unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> Death &amp; passion I hope for salvation.
                </p>
                <p>I give and bequeath unto my son <persName type="son" xml:id="RichardJonesJr">Richard <surname>Jones</surname></persName> item <measure commodity="livestock" ><unclear reason="illegible">cows</unclear> mare to
                    <lb/>be under three years of age</measure> and then to enjoy the benefit of his Estate in
                    <lb/>his own hands and to bee free from all servitude at he age of sixteen
                    <lb/>either from his mother or any other person whatsoever.
                </p>
                <p>I give and bequeath unto my Daughter <persName type="daughter">Ann <surname>Jones</surname></persName> <unclear reason="illegible">item</unclear> <measure commodity="livestock">cows more to bee
                <lb/>under three year old</measure> and to enjoy the Benefit of the <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> at sixteen years
                    <lb/>old and to have the free possession of them in her own hands to be free
                    <lb/>from all servitude either from her mother or any other person whatsoever
                    <lb/>that is if my son or Daughter will not stay with their mother after the
                    <lb/>age of sixteen and till they are ---- at sixteen they shall live
                    <lb/>with their mother.
                </p>
                <p>I give and bequeath to my son Richard <measure commodity="tool" quantity="1" xml:id="RichardJonesJr">one Iron hot</measure> <measure commodity="weapon" quantity="2" xml:id="RichardJonesJr">two guns</measure>
                    <lb/><measure commodity="houseware" quantity="6" xml:id="RichardJonesJr">six puter dishes</measure> &amp; <measure commodity="houseware" quantity="6" xml:id="RichardJonesJr">six silver plates</measure> <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> <measure commodity="horse"  quantity="1" xml:id="RichardJonesJr">one bat maire with
                    <lb/><unclear reason="illegible">ablaze</unclear> in her face aged about six years</measure> with her <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> and she and 
                    <lb/>her increase to <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> for the use of the said Richard &amp; Ann Jones well they 
                    <lb/><catchwords>come</catchwords>
                    <pb/>
                    <lb/>come at the age of sixteen and then the maine and her increase to bee
                    <lb/>equally divided between them
                </p>
                <p>I further more I doe make my loving wife <persName type="spouse" xml:id="JaneJones">Jane <surname>Jones</surname></persName> my whole &amp; sole
                    <lb/>Executor of all that worldly Estate that God hath been pleased to <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear>
                    <lb/>upon mee all my goods &amp; chattles within <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> and without &amp; desire
                    <lb/>what Debts in due to me &amp; likewise to pay all such Debts that I am
                    <lb/>indebted &amp; to bury me in a decent manner. all besdies what I give to my 
                    <lb/>Children.
                </p>
                <p>I doe now declare before God and the world what is Justly due to me that 
                    <lb/>is without <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear>.
                </p>
                <p><table>
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="HumphreyJones">Mr. Humphrey <surname>Jones</surname></persName> <measure quantity="400" xml:id="HumphreyJones">four hundred and <unclear reason="illegible">cask</unclear></measure>
                        </cell>
                        <cell>400</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="ThomasB">Thomas <surname><unclear reason="illegible">B</unclear></surname></persName> <measure quantity="490" xml:id="ThomasB">four hundred and ninety</measure>
                        </cell> 
                        <cell>490</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="JohnSmith">John <surname>Smith</surname></persName> Carpenter <measure quantity="1200" xml:id="JohnSmith">twelve hundred</measure>
                        </cell>
                        <cell>1200</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="JohnAllen"></persName> <measure quantity="400" xml:id="JohnAllen">four hundred</measure>
                        </cell>
                        <cell>400</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="DH"><unclear reason="illegible">D</unclear> <unclear reason="illegible">H</unclear></persName> <measure quantity="1360" xml:id="DH"></measure>thirteen hundred and sixty
                        </cell>
                        
                        <cell>1360</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="FrancisChumly">Francis <surname>Chumly</surname></persName> <measure quantity="462" xml:id="FranicChumly">four hundred and sixty two</measure>
                        </cell>
                        
                        <cell>462</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="DomindagoGambrell">Domindago Gambrell</persName></cell>
                        <cell><measure quantity="420" xml:id="DomindagoGambrell"></measure>420</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="MrDent">Mr. <surname>Dent</surname></persName></cell>
                        <cell><measure quantity="400" xml:id="MrDent"></measure>400</cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="RobertDoyner"></persName>Mr. Robert <surname>Doyner</surname></cell>
                    <cell><measure quantity="400" xml:id="RobertDoyner">400</measure></cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="RichardBowton">Richard <surname>Bowton</surname></persName></cell>
                    <cell><measure quantity="200" xml:id="RichardBowton">200</measure></cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="MrBread">Mr. <unclear reason="illegible">Bread</unclear></persName> <measure commodity="crop" quantity="3" xml:id="MrBread">Three Barrells od Corn</measure>
                        </cell> 
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="MrDais">Mr. <unclear reason="illegible">Daies</unclear></persName></cell>
                        <cell><measure quantity="400" xml:id="MrDais"></measure></cell>
                    </row>
                    
                    <row role="data">
                        <cell>Total</cell>
                        <cell>6132</cell>
                    </row>
                </table>
                </p>
                <p>In witness to the above mentioned <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> I doe hereunto set my hand and
                    <lb/>seal this present day being the <date>twenty sixth of January 1685</date>
                </p>
                <p>Signed Sealed &amp; Delivered
                    <lb/>his
                    <lb/><persName type="witness">Edward R <surname>Golf</surname></persName>
                    <lb/>mark
                    <lb/>his
                    <lb/><persName type="witness">Thomas <unclear><surname>Bumpop</surname></unclear></persName>
                    <lb/>mark
                    <lb/><persName type="witness">Edward <surname>Potter</surname></persName>
                    <lb/>my son to have three years schooling
                    <lb/><signatures>Richard R. Jones</signatures>
                </p>
                <pb/>
                <p>
                    <table>
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell><persName type="beneficiary" xml:id="RalphBarttlett">Ralph <surname>Barttlett</surname></persName></cell>
                        <cell>D.</cell>
                        </row>
                        
                        <row role="data">
                            <cell>To one pare of French <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear></cell>
                            <cell>070</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p>On the back of the foregoing was endorsed the following probate <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear>
                    <lb/><date>April the 19th 1686</date> then this within mentioned will was proved
                    <lb/>before me by the oaths of Edward Golf Thomas <unclear reason="illegible"></unclear> &amp;Edward Potter
                    <lb/>5 1/4 sides
                    <lb/><persName>John <surname>Stone</surname></persName>
                    
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
